    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is running beautifully, making it the perfect reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've kept up with everything so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
