    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. This unit delivers a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its composure through the M-Variable locking differential and aluminum subframes. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator updates, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system remain within tight tolerances. While showing minor signs of road-going use, the drivetrain remains robust and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited cornering and track-day reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Minimal wear.",
