    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and she\u2019s looking for a great new home! This car has been super dependable and is in wonderful shape for its next adventure. I\u2019ve always kept up with the maintenance, so it runs smoothly and looks great inside and out. It\u2019s the perfect blend of comfort and performance\u2014honestly, a joy to drive. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
